            "draft_value": "NASA Science has invested over $1.4 million in FL-14 since FY2023. Key local impacts include $272,545 in grants to The University of Tampa for lunar and Martian research and $1.1 million in contracts to American Wordata, Inc for critical data infrastructure.",
